    {
      "id": "section-header-grammar-defaults",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Default Policy",
      "position": {
        "x": 1260,
        "y": 520
      },
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 280,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Default Policy\n\n- a **header** names and orients a section\n- a **cluster** expresses containment\n- a **summary node** speaks outward\n- a named section is usually `header + members`, and for larger boards `header + cluster + members`\n- headers are **not connectable by default**\n- summary consumers replace plain navigation once a source can expose honest state",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
